54:05.280 --> 54:07.240
and I'll be there.

54:12.920 --> 54:16.160
-(CROWD CHATTERING)
-(DOG SNIFFING)

54:17.720 --> 54:19.920
ARTHUR: Beanie. Come on, boy.

54:20.040 --> 54:22.200
Get over here, you lazy bastard.

54:22.840 --> 54:26.080
Now, what's all that, eh? (LAUGHS)

54:26.200 --> 54:27.680
(SNIFFS)

54:27.760 --> 54:30.280
The room is, uh, clean, Mr Shelby.

54:30.360 --> 54:32.920
Right. Lock it all down.

54:34.120 --> 54:36.120
All right, boys. Lock her down.

54:44.440 --> 54:48.160
MAN: No weapons.
No admission if you've any weapons.

54:48.240 --> 54:50.080
You're good. Go on.

54:52.760 --> 54:54.360
(GRUNTS) Go on!

54:58.160 --> 54:59.320
MAN: Arthur!

55:00.760 --> 55:02.080
Can I open the book, can I?

55:02.160 --> 55:03.560
Right. Open it up.

55:03.840 --> 55:05.200
You.

55:10.080 --> 55:11.760
Gentlemen!

55:12.640 --> 55:15.480
ARTHUR: Now you listen to me.
You put all your money on the Gold.

55:15.560 --> 55:18.960
You hear me? Let's fucking fine dine.

55:20.080 --> 55:21.720
Oi, Jacko.

55:22.840 --> 55:27.760
Come on, boys,
and place your bets with me!

55:27.920 --> 55:30.040
Honest Johnny Dodds.

55:30.120 --> 55:32.360
The only show in town

55:32.480 --> 55:35.920
in order of
your special constable brothers,

55:36.000 --> 55:38.560
the Peaky fucking Blinders. (LAUGHS)

55:52.440 --> 55:53.840
ARTHUR: Bonnie boy!

55:54.280 --> 55:55.520
There we go, boy.

55:56.440 --> 55:59.280
Bring out that fucking tiger, eh?
Go on.

55:59.520 --> 56:00.920
Tiger's already out.

56:01.280 --> 56:02.600
Fair enough.

56:03.680 --> 56:07.120
Bonnie, Mr Shelby will give you
a 20% cut

56:07.200 --> 56:09.600
if you put Goliath down
in the fourth round.

56:10.240 --> 56:12.160
ARTHUR: Been caged up
too long, brother.

56:14.600 --> 56:17.680
If the women are going to have fun,
so am I!

56:37.920 --> 56:40.480
(CROWD CHATTERING)

57:30.920 --> 57:35.280
<i># On a gathering storm
comes a tall handsome man</i>

57:35.360 --> 57:39.840
<i># In a dusty black coat
with a red right hand #</i>

57:39.864 --> 57:44.864
http://hiqve.com/
